 those people. During the game, you will see the world through the eyes of the main character. Many puzzles await to be solved and many letters await to be read. The painter\u2019s journal gives us detailed information about his mental state and thoughts. Inquisitives will be able to find additional hints binding the story together.<br><br><img src=\"http://fatdoggames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/roomAnimowane.png\"><br><br><strong>Handmade graphic and music are important elements</strong> that add depth to story. The room changes accordingly to the mental state of a character. The game has multiple endings. <strong>How the story ends depends on the seemingly trivial decisions</strong> made by the player during the game.<br><br><img src=\"http://fatdoggames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/uniqueAnimowane.png\"><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deep, melancholy atmosphere thanks to high quality handmade art and originally composed soundtrack.<br></li><li>Intriguing story evolving at every subtle, seemingly trivial decision.<br></li><li>Engaging narrative with multiple endings depending on the decisions made by the player.<br></li><li>Unique, ever-changing room which reacts to the mental state of the main character.</li></ul>", "mac_requirements": [], "background": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/702600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1506512419", "movies": [{"webm": {"480": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693383/movie480.webm?t=1503658218", "max": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693383/movie_max.webm?t=1503658218"}, "name": "Indygo Greenlight Trailer (EN)", "thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693383/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1503658218", "highlight": true, "id": 256693383}, {"webm": {"480": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693384/movie480.webm?t=1503658237", "max": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693384/movie_max.webm?t=1503658237"}, "name": "Indygo teaser (EN)", "thumbna